Class PDAInitDBBTreeCmd

  • java.lang.Object
    • parallel.distributed.RRObject
      • parallel.distributed.PDAsynchInitCmd
        • graph.packing.PDAInitDBBTreeCmd
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PDAInitDBBTreeCmd
extends PDAsynchInitCmd
    auxiliary class NOT used for the initialization of distributed PDAsynchBatchTaskExecutorWrk objects running code for the distributed version of the BBGASPPacker. Not part of the public API. Will be removed.
